2026-05-11T21:25:37.5559319Z 13    <!--
2026-05-11T21:25:37.5559866Z 14        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-05-11T21:25:37.5561026Z 15        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
2026-05-11T21:25:37.5562246Z 16        Settings → Notifications. Android 14+ restricts this to apps whose
2026-05-11T21:25:37.5563122Z 17        core function is alarms/calendar/communication; for other apps the
2026-05-11T21:25:37.5564018Z 18        system downgrades it to a heads-up notification, which is fine —
