2026-05-11T21:25:37.5587264Z 22    <!--
2026-05-11T21:25:37.5587723Z 23        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-11T21:25:37.5588598Z 24        across Android versions:
2026-05-11T21:25:37.5589144Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-11T21:25:37.5589796Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-11T21:25:37.5590431Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-11T21:25:37.5591065Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-11T21:25:37.5591694Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-11T21:25:37.5592334Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-11T21:25:37.5592967Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-11T21:25:37.5593557Z 32        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-11T21:25:37.5594040Z 33    -->
2026-05-11T21:25:37.5594568Z 34    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM" />
